               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270531-210-person1177">
                  THOMAS 
                  DAY
               <interp inst="t18270531-210-person1177" type="surname" value="DAY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270531-210-person1177" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270531-210-person1177" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , SEN. I am the prisoner's father. I knew the box was at my house - I gave him no authority to pawn the articles - my sister asked leave to send some plate to my house - I saw the box there and concluded that it contained plate - I opened it and the hasp came off; I opened it because my son had left the house.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
